which Mole, Ratty and Toad are joined by Hedge, a young hedgehog with a zest for life.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"toad-friends-97474697\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474698\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T00:25:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T00:35:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Toad \u0026 Friends\",\"description\":\"Sail Away. It’s a stormy day and Toad ignores Ratty’s instructions to tie the sail down. The sail takes off, taking Ratty, Mole, and Hedge with it. Toad has to take to the skies himself in order to save his friends.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"toad-friends-97474698\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474699\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T00:35:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T00:50:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Toad \u0026 Friends\",\"description\":\"Do Not Disturb. It’s time for Addy to shed her itchy skin but the other riverbankers fail to understand why she is so grumpy and continually interrupt her peace and quiet.\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"toad-friends-97474699\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474700\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T00:50:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T01:00:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series II\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-ii-97474700\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474701\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T01:00:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T01:20:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series II\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":20,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-ii-97474701\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474702\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T01:20:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T01:30:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series II\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-ii-97474702\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474703\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T01:30:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T01:45:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series II\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-ii-97474703\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474704\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T01:45:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T01:55:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Interstellar Ella\",\"description\":\"In the year 3021, on a space station somewhere between Mars and Jupiter in the Milky Way, 8-year-old Ella Ryder sets out with her friends on exciting adventures of discovery.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"interstellar-ella-97474704\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474705\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T01:55:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T02:05:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Interstellar Ella\",\"description\":\"In the year 3021, on a space station somewhere between Mars and Jupiter in the Milky Way, 8-year-old Ella Ryder sets out with her friends on exciting adventures of discovery.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"interstellar-ella-97474705\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474706\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T02:05:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T02:25:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Interstellar Ella\",\"description\":\"In the year 3021, on a space station somewhere between Mars and Jupiter in the Milky Way, 8-year-old Ella Ryder sets out with her friends on exciting adventures of discovery.\",\"durationMin\":20,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"interstellar-ella-97474706\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474707\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T02:25:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T02:35:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Interstellar Ella\",\"description\":\"In the year 3021, on a space station somewhere between Mars and Jupiter in the Milky Way, 8-year-old Ella Ryder sets out with her friends on exciting adventures of discovery.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"interstellar-ella-97474707\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474708\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T02:35:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T02:45:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Interstellar Ella\",\"description\":\"In the year 3021, on a space station somewhere between Mars and Jupiter in the Milky Way, 8-year-old Ella Ryder sets out with her friends on exciting adventures of discovery.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"interstellar-ella-97474708\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474709\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T02:45:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T02:55:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Barney's World - Meet Barney\",\"description\":\"Meet Barney and his friends as they play in the park, share what makes them special, and explore their big emotions.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"barney-s-world-meet-barney-97474709\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474710\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T02:55:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T03:05:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Toad \u0026 Friends\",\"description\":\"Horse Power. Toad decides to actually ride his horse Mulberry as both his car and caravan are out of action. But riding a horse requires skills Toad simply hasn’t got.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"toad-friends-97474710\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474711\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T03:05:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T03:15:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Toad \u0026 Friends\",\"description\":\"Drip Drop. Toad’s violin recital is interrupted by the leaks from his roof. When Toad tries to fix it, he discovers the leaks have given him a musical bonus.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"toad-friends-97474711\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474712\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T03:15:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T03:30:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Toad \u0026 Friends\",\"description\":\"‘Toad and Friends’, based on Kenneth Grahame’s literary classic, ‘The Wind in The Willows’, is lovingly brought to life in a brand-new animated series for 4-7 year olds in which Mole, Ratty and Toad are joined by Hedge, a young hedgehog with a zest for life.\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"toad-friends-97474712\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474713\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T03:30:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T03:40:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Toad \u0026 Friends\",\"description\":\"Sail Away. It’s a stormy day and Toad ignores Ratty’s instructions to tie the sail down. The sail takes off, taking Ratty, Mole, and Hedge with it. Toad has to take to the skies himself in order to save his friends.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"toad-friends-97474713\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474714\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T03:40:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T04:00:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Toad \u0026 Friends\",\"description\":\"Do Not Disturb. It’s time for Addy to shed her itchy skin but the other riverbankers fail to understand why she is so grumpy and continually interrupt her peace and quiet.\",\"durationMin\":20,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"toad-friends-97474714\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474715\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T04:00:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T04:05:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings IV\",\"description\":\"Jungle Rhythm. The Lemmings organize a dance contest where the first prize is a jar of chocolate spread. Grizzy is hungry and decides to participate. He partners up with a talented dancing parrot and wins. Incapable of sharing, Grizzy and the Lemmings fight over the prize. The parrot brings the jar to a temple devoted to the glory of dancing parrots. To get it back, Grizzy and the Lemmings must perform a choreography. They decide to rehearse together.\",\"durationMin\":5,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iv-97474715\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474716\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T04:05:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T04:10:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings IV\",\"description\":\"The Grizming. Grizzy finds a strange creature fossilized in amber resin that resembles him. A natural science encyclopedia confirms that it’s his ancestor. Grizzy wants to take the block of amber, but the Lemmings fight him for it because the blue animal with big teeth is their ancestor too. The block cracks during their fight and frees the ancestor who turns out to be a rather unmanageable burden.\",\"durationMin\":5,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iv-97474716\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474717\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T04:10:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T04:25:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings IV\",\"description\":\"For Real. The Lemmings find a strange card game representing the elements along with instructions. The idea is to pretend that the ground is on fire or of ice, like in the game “Floor is Lava.” They transform the cabin into a giant adventure trail. Depending on the card drawn, they must avoid zones on the floor with flames or wax. Grizzy unceremoniously gets rids of the setup to regain control of the cabin. One of the cards lands on a stone slab that transforms into lava. The Lemmings are delighted: they will be able to play “for real”!\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iv-97474717\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474718\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T04:25:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T04:35:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings IV\",\"description\":\"Cocoa Tree Spread. The Lemmings discover a very particular cocoa tree with chocolate-spread sap! Reduced to eating canned Brussels sprouts, the only remaining food in the cabin, Grizzy is baffled when he sees the Lemmings parading past to equip themselves with all sorts of containers: ladles, soup spoons, bowls, buckets, basins, etc. He watches them through binoculars and discovers that they have planted a faucet in a tree where chocolate spread flows. Grizzy decides to siphon off their tree.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iv-97474718\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474719\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T04:35:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T04:40:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings IV\",\"description\":\"Wild Mutations. Grizzy expels the Lemmings from the cabin where they had built a cumbersome obstacle course. Peaceful at last and feeling lazy, he is determined not to leave his couch. The Lemmings discover a magic Mayan disc that allows you to choose instantaneous mutations of other animals’ features: bat wings, reindeer antlers, elephant trunks, etc. The mutant Lemmings return to the cabin, determined to continue playing their game while enjoying their new accessories.\",\"durationMin\":5,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iv-97474719\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474720\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T04:40:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T04:55:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"SuperThings: Rivals of Kaboom - Kazoom Power\",\"description\":\"Kai, Finn, and Mia find themselves thrust into the adventure of their lives when Enigma calls upon them to travel to Kaboom City.\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"superthings-rivals-of-kaboom-kazoom-power-97474720\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474721\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T04:55:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T05:05:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Bugs Bunny Builders\",\"description\":\"Smash House. The Looney Builders learn that Taz accidentally destroyed his house, so they set out to build him a new one that’s smash-proof.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"bugs-bunny-builders-97474721\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474722\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T05:05:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T05:25:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Bugs Bunny Builders\",\"description\":\"Play Day. When the Looney Builders build themselves a playground, Daffy gets so excited about his section that he takes all the supplies for himself.\",\"durationMin\":20,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"bugs-bunny-builders-97474722\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474723\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T05:25:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T05:35:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Batwheels\",\"description\":\"Cave Sweet Cave. After the Joker floods the Batcave, the Batwheels evacuate and relocate to a nearby parking garage. As they adapt to their temporary home, they learn important lessons about family and making the most of what you have.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"batwheels-97474723\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474724\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T05:35:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T05:55:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Batwheels\",\"description\":\"Scaredy-Bat. When Batman refuses to engage Joker in a race, Prank goads Bam into a rematch. Can Bam learn to not give in to the bully's dares and take the high road?\",\"durationMin\":20,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"batwheels-97474724\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474725\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T05:55:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T06:20:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Be Cool, Scooby-Doo! II\",\"description\":\"This time, the gang is working as hard to solve their own personal problems as they are in solving the endless, mind-bending mysteries that await them.\",\"durationMin\":25,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"be-cool-scooby-doo-ii-97474725\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474726\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T06:20:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T06:50:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Be Cool, Scooby-Doo! II\",\"description\":\"This time, the gang is working as hard to solve their own personal problems as they are in solving the endless, mind-bending mysteries that await them.\",\"durationMin\":30,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"be-cool-scooby-doo-ii-97474726\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474727\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T06:50:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T07:00:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-97474727\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474728\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T07:00:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T07:20:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series IV\",\"description\":\"Mr Bean returns for a fourth series of his animated adventures. This series follows Mr Bean, his best friend Teddy and his long-suffering landlady Mrs Wicket as we witness more of the mishaps that surround Mr Bean's daily life.\",\"durationMin\":20,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-iv-97474728\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474729\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T07:20:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T07:30:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series II\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-ii-97474729\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474730\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T07:30:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T07:40:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series II\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-ii-97474730\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474731\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T07:40:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T08:00:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series II\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":20,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-ii-97474731\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474732\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T08:00:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T08:05:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Lamput IV\",\"description\":\"Lamput is a gooey orange nutcase that has escaped from the asylum! Two Docs are out to get him, but the problem is they can never catch him becasue Lamput is a master of disguise!\",\"durationMin\":5,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"lamput-iv-97474732\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474733\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T08:05:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T08:10:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Lamput IV\",\"description\":\"Lamput is a gooey orange nutcase that has escaped from the asylum! Two Docs are out to get him, but the problem is they can never catch him becasue Lamput is a master of disguise!\",\"durationMin\":5,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"lamput-iv-97474733\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474734\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T08:10:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T08:25:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Lamput III\",\"description\":\"Arm Wrestling. The Boss takes on a particularly enormous sailor in a seedy underground arm wrestling tournament. Who knew old Boss such grit?\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"lamput-iii-97474734\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474735\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T08:25:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T08:30:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings II\",\"description\":\"Hocus Pocus Lemmingus. The Lemmings discover an old book of magic spells with a formula that enables one to take on the appearance of any other creature. The Lemmings have the bright idea of transforming one their kin into a double of the she-bear Grizzy is madly in love with in order to trick him. How could Grizzy refuse to give his jar of chocolate spread to his sweetheart?\",\"durationMin\":5,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-ii-97474735\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474736\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T08:30:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T08:40:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings III\",\"description\":\"Lemming Fortune. When Grizzy propels the Lemmings out of the log cabin perched on the Great Wall of China, the critters land on a small traditional house in a bamboo forest where they discover a box filled with fortune cookies. One Lemming gets super lucky after eating one. Armed with their magic cookies, the Lemmings set out to confront Grizzy. But each cookie represents a power… or a curse!\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iii-97474736\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474737\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T08:40:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T08:50:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings III\",\"description\":\"Tough Medicine. The Lemmings love sesame nougat but Grizzy, who adores this treat too, steals their box. Quite upset, the rodents search for more, in vain. Instead, they discover the art of energy points in an old Chinese medicine book. Determined to recover their sweets regardless of the cost, the Lemmings activate Grizzy's vital points and the bear finds himself completely blocked. Thanks to the book, Grizzy frees himself and learns to master energies in turn.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iii-97474737\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474738\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T08:50:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T09:00:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings III\",\"description\":\"Tai Chi Lemmings. After a game that ends abruptly, the Lemmings fall onto the roof of a temple where they discover drawings of Tai Chi movements. When carried out, the exercises generate a ball of energy! The Lemmings test out the sequence of movements on… Grizzy, until he is evicted from the cabin and falls onto the temple in turn. His fall unveils a new sequence of movements on a fresco that could create an even stronger energy flow!\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iii-97474738\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474739\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T09:00:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T09:05:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings III\",\"description\":\"Domestic Shaolin. After being thrown out of the log cabin by Grizzy, the Lemmings find a dragon statue with a mysterious stone in a temple. Touching the stone makes a fleeting tattoo appear on their bellies, temporarily endowing them with the mastery of Shaolin Kung Fu. The Lemmings return to the cabin and uproot Grizzy with ease! But Grizzy has not said his last word and manages to get hold of the magic stone.\",\"durationMin\":5,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iii-97474739\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474740\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T09:05:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T09:20:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings III\",\"description\":\"Peaceable Enemies. Grizzy and the Lemmings fight over the tablet. During their scuffle, they knock over an army crate which falls into the middle of the bamboo forest surrounding the cabin. Alerted by the noise, a peace missionary panda comes out of the forest and tries to calm down the worked-up adversaries. But will the limitless strategies of Grizzy and the Lemmings get the better of the panda's patience?\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iii-97474740\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474741\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T09:20:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T09:25:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"The Tom and Jerry Show III\",\"description\":\"The iconic cat and mouse rivals are back. The all-new series takes another look at the madcap slapstick and never-ending battle that has made Tom and Jerry two of the most beloved characters of all time.\",\"durationMin\":5,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"the-tom-and-jerry-show-iii-97474741\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474742\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T09:25:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T09:35:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"The Tom and Jerry Show III\",\"description\":\"The iconic cat and mouse rivals are back. The all-new series takes another look at the madcap slapstick and never-ending battle that has made Tom and Jerry two of the most beloved characters of all time.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"the-tom-and-jerry-show-iii-97474742\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474743\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T09:35:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T09:50:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"The Tom and Jerry Show III\",\"description\":\"The iconic cat and mouse rivals are back. The all-new series takes another look at the madcap slapstick and never-ending battle that has made Tom and Jerry two of the most beloved characters of all time.\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"the-tom-and-jerry-show-iii-97474743\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474744\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T09:50:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T09:55:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"The Tom and Jerry Show III\",\"description\":\"Bars and Stripes. After catching a crook, Tom and Jerry are framed, and the police chase them instead of the true criminal. Tom and Jerry must go on the lam as they try to avoid jail time.\",\"durationMin\":5,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"the-tom-and-jerry-show-iii-97474744\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474745\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T09:55:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T10:00:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"The Tom and Jerry Show III\",\"description\":\"The iconic cat and mouse rivals are back. The all-new series takes another look at the madcap slapstick and never-ending battle that has made Tom and Jerry two of the most beloved characters of all time.\",\"durationMin\":5,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"the-tom-and-jerry-show-iii-97474745\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474746\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T10:00:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T10:15:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"The Tom and Jerry Show III\",\"description\":\"The iconic cat and mouse rivals are back. The all-new series takes another look at the madcap slapstick and never-ending battle that has made Tom and Jerry two of the most beloved characters of all time.\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"the-tom-and-jerry-show-iii-97474746\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474747\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T10:15:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T10:25:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series IV\",\"description\":\"Mr Bean returns for a fourth series of his animated adventures. This series follows Mr Bean, his best friend Teddy and his long-suffering landlady Mrs Wicket as we witness more of the mishaps that surround Mr Bean's daily life.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-iv-97474747\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474748\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T10:25:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T10:45:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series II\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":20,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-ii-97474748\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474749\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T10:45:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T10:55:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series II\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-ii-97474749\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474750\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T10:55:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T11:15:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series II\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":20,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-ii-97474750\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474751\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T11:15:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T11:25:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-97474751\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474752\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T11:25:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T11:35:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-97474752\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474753\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T11:35:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T11:50:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series II\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-ii-97474753\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474754\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T11:50:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T12:05:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series II\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-ii-97474754\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474755\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T12:05:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T12:15:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series II\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-ii-97474755\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474756\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T12:15:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T12:30:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series IV\",\"description\":\"Mr Bean returns for a fourth series of his animated adventures. This series follows Mr Bean, his best friend Teddy and his long-suffering landlady Mrs Wicket as we witness more of the mishaps that surround Mr Bean's daily life.\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-iv-97474756\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474757\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T12:30:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T12:39:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Lamput IV\",\"description\":\"Lamput is a gooey orange nutcase that has escaped from the asylum! Two Docs are out to get him, but the problem is they can never catch him becasue Lamput is a master of disguise!\",\"durationMin\":9,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"lamput-iv-97474757\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474758\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T12:39:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T12:45:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Lamput III\",\"description\":\"The Chase. Lamput escapes from the Lab, the Boss gives the job of orange-blob-retrieval to Doc Specs and Doc Skinny, who turn out to really suck at orange-blob-retrieval.\",\"durationMin\":6,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"lamput-iii-97474758\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474759\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T12:45:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T13:00:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Lamput IV\",\"description\":\"Lamput is a gooey orange nutcase that has escaped from the asylum! Two Docs are out to get him, but the problem is they can never catch him becasue Lamput is a master of disguise!\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"lamput-iv-97474759\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474760\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T13:00:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T13:10:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Bugs Bunny Builders II\",\"description\":\"Cake Bake. The Looney Builders take turns distracting Petunia as they build her a big surprise birthday cake in the back yard.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"bugs-bunny-builders-ii-97474760\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474761\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T13:10:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T13:20:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Bugs Bunny Builders II\",\"description\":\"Porky Perfect Parade. The Looney Builders build a float to lead the Flower Parade, but Porky won’t settle for anything less than Porky Perfect.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"bugs-bunny-builders-ii-97474761\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474762\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T13:20:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T13:30:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Bugs Bunny Builders: Hard Hat Time\",\"description\":\"Bugs Bunny Boogie. Bugs Bunny uses his excavator to dig in this music video as he tackles looney jobs across town.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"bugs-bunny-builders-hard-hat-time-97474762\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474763\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T13:30:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T13:40:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Batwheels II\",\"description\":\"Batwheels, a preschool animated action-adventure comedy series starring the most heroic and iconic vehicles from the DC universe. They are a team of incredible crimefighters who have banded together to oppose evil, combat crime and clean up the streets of Gotham City. They are...okay, they're NOT Batman and Robin. They're the Batwheels - an awesome group of sentient super-powered crime-fighting vehicles defending Gotham City alongside Batman, Robin, Batgirl and a host of DC Super Heroes. Having just been created by the Batcomputer, our heroes are essentially kids with little to no life experience. Led by Bam (The Batmobile), the Batwheels - Bibi (The Batgirl Cycle), Red (The Redbird), Jett (The Batwing) and Buff (The Bat Truck) - must navigate the growing pains of being a newly formed super team as well as the growing pains that come with just being a kid.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"batwheels-ii-97474763\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474764\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T13:40:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T14:00:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Batwheels II\",\"description\":\"MOE Alone. A sneaky trick strands the Batwheels at the docks, clearing the way for a Batcave heist by the Legion of Zoom. It’s up to MOE to stop the Zoomers with zany improvised tricks and traps with a little help from Ace and Batcomputer.\",\"durationMin\":20,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"batwheels-ii-97474764\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474765\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T14:00:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T14:25:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Be Cool, Scooby-Doo!\",\"description\":\"With high school over, Shaggy, Scooby, Velma, Daphne and Fred decide to travel during what could be their last summer break together. The gang hits the road in the Mystery Machine, chasing fun and adventure.\",\"durationMin\":25,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"be-cool-scooby-doo-97474765\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474766\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T14:25:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T14:55:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Be Cool, Scooby-Doo!\",\"description\":\"With high school over, Shaggy, Scooby, Velma, Daphne and Fred decide to travel during what could be their last summer break together. The gang hits the road in the Mystery Machine, chasing fun and adventure.\",\"durationMin\":30,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"be-cool-scooby-doo-97474766\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474767\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T14:55:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T15:05:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series IV\",\"description\":\"Mr Bean returns for a fourth series of his animated adventures. This series follows Mr Bean, his best friend Teddy and his long-suffering landlady Mrs Wicket as we witness more of the mishaps that surround Mr Bean's daily life.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-iv-97474767\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474768\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T15:05:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T15:25:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series III\",\"description\":\"Cat Chaos. Mrs. Wicket becomes annoyingly inconsolable when Scrapper goes missing – calling for him at all hours of the day and night. Bean can’t get any sleep! He decides that the only way to restore peace in the household is to go out and find Scrapper himself – a journey that takes him deep into London’s sewers …\",\"durationMin\":20,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-iii-97474768\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474769\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T15:25:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T15:35:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series III\",\"description\":\"Stick It. Bean discovers Mrs. Wicket’s nephew and Bruiser Jnr swapping football stickers and decides that he wants to fill up a sticker album too. He buys-up all the stickers in the neighbourhood and has almost completed his task when Nephew points out that he’s missing one: the famous sticker owned by local footballing celebrity Jamie Studds. Bean turns thief to be the best collector of ‘em all.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-iii-97474769\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474770\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T15:35:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T15:45:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series III\",\"description\":\"Bean at the Museum. Mr. Bean thinks he’s just dug up a valuable coin in the back-garden and goes rushing off to the Museum to have it valued little knowing that it’s actually Bruiser Snr’s much-loved but valueless fake gold medallion. Bruiser Snr wants it back; and forces Bean to break back into the Museum to get it.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-iii-97474770\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474771\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T15:45:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T15:55:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Lamput III\",\"description\":\"Lamput is a gooey orange nutcase that has escaped from the asylum! Two Docs are out to get him, but the problem is they can never catch him becasue Lamput is a master of disguise!\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"lamput-iii-97474771\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474772\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T15:55:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T16:00:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings IV\",\"description\":\"Grasshopper Bounty. The Lemmings catch a grasshopper that can give you whatever your heart desires in abundance. All you need to do is set the grasshopper on its head while concentrating hard on what you want. As discretion is not the Lemmings’ strong point, Grizzy ends up understanding where their profusion of toys is coming from. Grizzy decides that it’s his turn to hunt down the grasshopper.\",\"durationMin\":5,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iv-97474772\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474773\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T16:00:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T16:10:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings IV\",\"description\":\"Choco-Noodles. Grizzy and the Lemmings are hungry! While fighting over a jar of Yummy chocolate spread, the jar is destroyed. But Grizzy discovers an ingenious manner to recover the remains of another Yummy jar using instant Chinese noodles as inspiration. The result is delicious. Grizzy and the Lemmings will once again fight over this new Yummy-based recipe: Choco-noodles.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iv-97474773\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474774\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T16:10:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T16:25:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings IV\",\"description\":\"Star Of The Day. While climbing back to the cabin carrying a load of delicious berries, Grizzy trips and falls over backwards. He performs a series of acrobatics worthy of a diving champ and resurfaces safe and sound despite himself. The Lemmings, who saw everything, are in awe and treat Grizzy like an idol. Grizzy starts to enjoy this VIP treatment until the Lemmings ask him to repeat his exploit. Grizzy agrees but discovers that the Lemmings have built a giant diving board for the occasion.\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iv-97474774\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474775\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T16:25:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T16:30:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings IV\",\"description\":\"Diabolical Labyrinth. Grizzy and the Lemmings lose their jar of chocolate spread in a labyrinthian Temple. Determined to recover their favorite afternoon snack, they confront one another in the maze, but end up getting totally lost. Grizzy finds himself back at square one and decides to find something to make holes in the walls and cheat. As for the Lemmings, they discover a magic map of the place that enables you to orient yourself and modify the corridors in real time. Which cheater will win?\",\"durationMin\":5,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iv-97474775\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474776\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T16:30:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T16:35:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings IV\",\"description\":\"Cozy Nest. Things start to disappear from the log cabin as if by magic. Grizzy is persuaded that the Lemmings are the culprits, but the Lemmings are also victims of inexplicable thefts. As they argue, Grizzy and the Lemmings discover the true authors of the repeated thefts: a gang of fanatic partridges who bring stolen objects as offerings to their goddess, a giant partridge. Grizzy and Lemmings join forces to infiltrate the nest and recover their belongings.\",\"durationMin\":5,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iv-97474776\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474777\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T16:35:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T16:45:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings IV\",\"description\":\"Strong Will. A frog swallows an ancestral jewel that bestows it with the power of mind control. Grizzy uses the frog to swallow the flies that have proliferated in the cabin, and which now let themselves be docilely caught. The Lemmings don’t miss a thing. They decide to get hold of the frog to hypnotize an uncooperative tapir who refuses to play rodeo. Grizzy hypnotizes the Lemmings, who become his servants. But several Lemmings escaped and are preparing a rescue mission.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iv-97474777\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474778\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T16:45:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T17:00:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"SuperThings: Rivals of Kaboom - Kazoom Power\",\"description\":\"One Of Us. Kid Fury faces Mr. King’s three challenges to prove his worth and show that he is the strongest.\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"superthings-rivals-of-kaboom-kazoom-power-97474778\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474779\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T17:00:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T17:30:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Be Cool, Scooby-Doo! II\",\"description\":\"This time, the gang is working as hard to solve their own personal problems as they are in solving the endless, mind-bending mysteries that await them.\",\"durationMin\":30,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"be-cool-scooby-doo-ii-97474779\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474780\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T17:30:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T18:00:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Be Cool, Scooby-Doo! II\",\"description\":\"This time, the gang is working as hard to solve their own personal problems as they are in solving the endless, mind-bending mysteries that await them.\",\"durationMin\":30,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"be-cool-scooby-doo-ii-97474780\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474781\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T18:00:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T18:10:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series IV\",\"description\":\"Mr Bean returns for a fourth series of his animated adventures. This series follows Mr Bean, his best friend Teddy and his long-suffering landlady Mrs Wicket as we witness more of the mishaps that surround Mr Bean's daily life.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-iv-97474781\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474782\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T18:10:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T18:25:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series II\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-ii-97474782\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474783\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T18:25:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T18:35:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series II\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-ii-97474783\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474784\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T18:35:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T18:55:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Mr Bean: The Animated Series\",\"description\":\"Join the strange but hilariously funny Mr Bean and his stuffed teddy on adventures such as avoiding an irate landlady or an evil one-eyed cat.\",\"durationMin\":20,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"mr-bean-the-animated-series-97474784\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474785\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T18:55:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T19:00:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings III\",\"description\":\"Thermal Lemmings. By chance, Grizzy and the Lemmings discover a container filled with metal survival food flasks. Primarily filled with vegetables, they do not find favor with the bear, who is more interested in the hi-tech equipment at the rear of the container. Behind his back, the Lemmings find a flask of Yummy and skedaddle with it. But how will they escape Grizzy equipped with his sophisticated gear?\",\"durationMin\":5,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iii-97474785\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474786\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T19:00:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T19:10:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings III\",\"description\":\"Substitute Egg. In a trunk, Grizzy and the Lemmings discover a big chocolate egg with a surprise inside. They are licking their lips. As they fight, they accidentally send the coveted egg flying amidst a group of penguins where a couple of winged creatures adopt it. They sit on the egg as if it were their offspring. Not intimidated, Grizzy and the Lemmings decide to get their hands on it, but the entire bird colony intervenes.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iii-97474786\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474787\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T19:10:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T19:25:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings III\",\"description\":\"Lemmings Constellation. The Lemmings open a nightclub with blasting music and a disco ball in an igloo they have built not far from the cabin. The noise prevents Grizzy from sleeping. The bear confiscates the disco ball and propels the Lemmings far into the distance. They land in an ice cave where they discover a console that lights up the stars in the sky and controls the northern lights. The canopy of heaven starts blinking. The Lemmings transform the ice field into an open-air discotheque!\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iii-97474787\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474788\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T19:25:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T19:30:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings III\",\"description\":\"Spinning Lemmings. The Lemmings come up with a ride worthy of a county fair in the living room. Awakened, Grizzy throws their juice extractor out the window and the rodents land in the neighboring science station where they accidentally wake up… a mammoth! A friendship is born between them. The Lemmings drag the mastodon into their game, and he transforms the entire cabin into a Ferris Wheel. Grizzy, who was trying to doze in peace, wakes up in a panic.\",\"durationMin\":5,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iii-97474788\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474789\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T19:30:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T19:35:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings III\",\"description\":\"Polar Super Star. Before an audience of penguins and walruses, two teams of Lemmings perform acrobatic high jumps, competing for the winning prize. When Grizzy accidentally jumps in, he quickly gets caught up in the game and the clapometer goes wild! Intoxicated by his victory, the bear is by no means a modest winner! But the Lemmings want their moment of glory in the limelight as well!\",\"durationMin\":5,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iii-97474789\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474790\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T19:35:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T19:45:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings III\",\"description\":\"My Friend The Penguin. While Grizzy fishes, a penguin comes over and sees that the bear's bucket is empty. He decides to help him and catches piles of fish. Impressed, the bear brings the penguin back to the cabin, where a friendship rapidly strikes up. This pleasant and friendly new companion quickly arouses the Lemmings' curiosity. They lure the penguin away on the sly and replace him with another one who's not nearly as clever. Grizzy will quickly see through the trickery.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iii-97474790\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474791\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T19:45:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T20:00:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Grizzy and The Lemmings III\",\"description\":\"Thermal Shock! Just as Grizzy settles into the couch by the fireside, the Lemmings come charging into the living room on their new mount, the vacuum cleaner. Irritated, the bear throws the mechanical charger into the fireplace, which blows up. Freezing air sweeps into the cabin. Seeking a source of heat, Grizzy decides to move into the science station greenhouse where the temperature is controlled by a drone. But the bear is unaware of what he carries in his luggage: the Lemmings!\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"grizzy-and-the-lemmings-iii-97474791\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474792\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T20:00:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T20:10:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Batwheels II\",\"description\":\"Clay Date. Clayface, Gotham City's messiest villain, arrives to cause trouble during Gotham's annual Clean Up Day. Redbird must overcome his fear of taking baths if he's going to help Bam bring Clayface to justice.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"batwheels-ii-97474792\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474793\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T20:10:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T20:25:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Batwheels II\",\"description\":\"Wish Upon a Car. Buff makes a wish on a magic artifact for the other Batwheels to be turned into monster trucks, just like him! The rest of the Batwheels must learn how to use their big new bodies to undo the wish!\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"batwheels-ii-97474793\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474794\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T20:25:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T20:35:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Batwheels II\",\"description\":\"Bibi's Bat-Belt Blunder. Bibi just can’t put down her new exciting video game, even when MOE needs her help packing Bam’s utility belt for a mission. Can she overcome the enticing distraction to save the day when Bam’s mis-packed belt goes haywire?\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"batwheels-ii-97474794\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474795\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T20:35:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T20:50:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Batwheels II\",\"description\":\"Lend Me Your Volunteer. Buff tries to show Batwing how great it is to volunteer to help Gotham's needy, but the Legion of Zoom get in the way.\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"batwheels-ii-97474795\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474796\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T20:50:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T21:05:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Bugs Bunny Builders\",\"description\":\"Blast Off. When Marvin the Martian crash lands in Looneyburg, he’s in a hurry to leave and hires The Looney Builders to build him a spaceship.\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"bugs-bunny-builders-97474796\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474797\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T21:05:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T21:20:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Bugs Bunny Builders\",\"description\":\"K-9: Space Puppy. Marvin the Martian hires The Looney Builders to build a doghouse on Mars for his puppy, K-9. Daffy soon bonds with K-9 and comes up with a plan to prolong their playtime.\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"bugs-bunny-builders-97474797\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474798\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T21:20:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T21:30:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Bugs Bunny Builders\",\"description\":\"Cousin Billy. When Daffy’s cool cousin Billy hires The Looney Builders to build her an art studio, Daffy tries to show off to prove how cool he is.\",\"durationMin\":10,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"bugs-bunny-builders-97474798\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474799\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T21:30:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T21:45:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"Bugs Bunny Builders\",\"description\":\"Cheddar Days. The Mouse Sisters hire The Looney Builders to build a cheese café featuring a mural by Sylvester who is having a bad day.\",\"durationMin\":15,\"genre\":null,\"slug\":\"bugs-bunny-builders-97474799\",\"channelId\":\"73\"},{\"id\":\"97474800\",\"start\":\"2025-10-13T21:45:00.000Z\",\"stop\":\"2025-10-13T21:55:00.000Z\",\"title\":\"The Tom and Jerry Show I